{"tid":1769140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】內地通報首10月拘逾600港人 拒講有否包括抗爭者","createTime":"2019-12-04T15:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T06:51:46.000Z","uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1521b6b2fcc22c081abaf52e8ceefd87f51830","tid":1769140,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"英國駐港總領事館前職員鄭文傑今年8月被深圳公安以「嫖妓」罪名行政拘留15天，回港後踢爆曾受公安酷刑虐待，更揭發有港示威者被送內地拷問。保安局局長李家超回覆議員提問時透露，根據香港與內地相互通報機制，今年首10個月，內地通報單位作出799次有關香港居民被採取強制措施的通報，涉及611名香港居民，罪行包括涉嫌吸毒、詐騙及走私等。但有關數字未有提及當中有否涉及曾參與遊行示威的個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191204/60341497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191204%2F60341497&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1ezyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=b10ef038\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191204%2F60341497&h=08048c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191204/60341497</a>"},{"pid":"2794b9076e229597da05fbc6211059a0db023dab","tid":1769140,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f5e7aaa9aa510e83a8d86162b4e4057c85af1ac8","tid":1769140,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2794b9076e229597da05fbc6211059a0db023dab","tid":1769140,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":2